					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Everything is doable, you only need either skills and knowledge how to do that, or money to get someone to make this done for you. You can't get the knowledge and skills with just reading few posts on a forum, this requires a lot of time and dedication.
<br />
<br />Also, you actually need to do two separate, unconnected things - hack a game and put it onto a cartridge. First requires knowledge of software, second requires knowledge or hardware (or just money to get PowerPak).</div>

					
